  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/bb118cc3073d1a4f18383eb145eeed6f.avif?t=1687085361\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras_big/bb118cc3073d1a4f18383eb145eeed6f.avif?t=1687085361 width=800 height=72 /></span><br><br><strong><u>What's going on?</u></strong><br><br>The Realm of Odaria has been thrown into disarray after brothers Prince Forlin and Prince Hagar launch an invasion. Cedric whose family has been scattered across the realm has made it his goal to save his family and take back their home in Haffenden.<br><br><strong><u>Action Based Combat</u></strong><br><br>Take full control of Cedric in battle with the action based combat system implemented in the game. Whether you attack, use your shield or use items, the choice is yours!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8140837ff1d642f5a0207c9aa0066283.poster.avif?t=1687085361\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8140837ff1d642f5a0207c9aa0066283.webm?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8140837ff1d642f5a0207c9aa0066283.mp4?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8a8f137ab19520f58b9321f2ab7978cb.poster.avif?t=1687085361\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8a8f137ab19520f58b9321f2ab7978cb.webm?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8a8f137ab19520f58b9321f2ab7978cb.mp4?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Custom Soundtrack</u></strong><br><br>Traverse around the various locations in Odaria and take in the unique sounds that will help immerse you in the world.<br><br><strong><u>There's more going on!</u></strong><br><br>The kingdoms in Odaria have a wide variety of issues plaguing them alongside the ultimate threat of invasion. Help rebuild them, solve puzzles, stop criminals and even collect and upgrade your armour to assist in the many battles you will face.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/de161915126d00ee1df12cb8252962aa.poster.avif?t=1687085361\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/de161915126d00ee1df12cb8252962aa.webm?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/de161915126d00ee1df12cb8252962aa.mp4?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>   - Hours of fun <br>   - In-game support for both keyboard and controller<br>   - Vibrant, colourful 2d style world<br>   - Compelling Story<br>   - Plenty of additional side activities",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/bb118cc3073d1a4f18383eb145eeed6f.avif?t=1687085361\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras_big/bb118cc3073d1a4f18383eb145eeed6f.avif?t=1687085361 width=800 height=72 /></span><br><br><strong><u>What's going on?</u></strong><br><br>The Realm of Odaria has been thrown into disarray after brothers Prince Forlin and Prince Hagar launch an invasion. Cedric whose family has been scattered across the realm has made it his goal to save his family and take back their home in Haffenden.<br><br><strong><u>Action Based Combat</u></strong><br><br>Take full control of Cedric in battle with the action based combat system implemented in the game. Whether you attack, use your shield or use items, the choice is yours!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8140837ff1d642f5a0207c9aa0066283.poster.avif?t=1687085361\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8140837ff1d642f5a0207c9aa0066283.webm?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8140837ff1d642f5a0207c9aa0066283.mp4?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8a8f137ab19520f58b9321f2ab7978cb.poster.avif?t=1687085361\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889960/extras/8a8f137ab19520f58b9321f2ab7978cb.webm?t=1687085361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source 